data.description: NEW LISTING IN WOODLAND HILLS:Take a look at this very spacious 4 Bedroom Home with 3 Full Baths.Beautiful Entrance leads to Great Room with Cathedral Ceiling & lots of natural lighting.Formal Dining Room has Bay Window,Gourmet Kitchen with Granite Countertops,lots of Cabinets & Stainless Appliances,Breakfast Nook has lots of windows.Patio Doors off Great Room with large wooden deck & beautiful view of the Ozark Hills.Master Suite & 2 Additional Bedrooms on the Main Floor.Master Suite has Vaulted Ceiling, Large Walk-In Closet,& Master Bath with Double Vanities,Large Jetted Tub, & Separate Shower.Finished Lower Level Includes Cozy Family Room with Gas Fireplace,4th Bedroom, & 3rd Full Bath.Mud Room is located off Garage & Utility Room.Wooden Privacy Fence in Back Yard. Newer Roof, & New Heat Pump.Water Softner Included.Owner will provide a $5000 floor covering allowance with full price offer. Electric Fireplace in Great Room is excluded. Enjoy country living with all city Amenities.
